channel.title: Orig317 Source Development
channel.description:
Source Name: Orig317 Source My Goal: To create a new 317 source, that is easy for beginner java coders to edit, and learn. I want this source to be a replica of the 317 Framework of RuneScape. Once that is completed, the people wanting to use this source can make the changes that they would have wanted to RuneScape.
What I Need to begin:
a.) Approval of Moderator for this team to be started.
and the following positions:
-Server Coder- -Server Coder- -Web Designer- -Web Graphics Designer-
Please get back to me as soon as possible, thanks.
